Package org.hrw.config

Record Class ConfigRecord

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
org.hrw.config.ConfigRecord
public record ConfigRecord(String mappingPath, String hashAlgorithm, int hashIntervalMinutes, String collectorServerIp, int jobInterval, String databaseIp, int databasePort, String blockchainUrl, byte blockchainChainId, String blockchainAddress, int databaseApiPort, String auditToolIp) extends Record
Immutable configuration container representing all application-relevant settings loaded from the config.properties file.

This record aggregates configuration parameters used by:

  • the data collector (server IP, job interval)
  • the hashing component (algorithm, interval)
  • the database connection (IP, port)
  • the blockchain anchoring service (URL, chain ID, address)
  • the embedded database API (port)
  • the audit tool (IP address)

All fields are required and must be present in the configuration file loaded by ConfigLoader.
